text:
...Hmm? Ah, yeah, that's right.
At night, it's dark, so you can't really see much.

...What's wrong?
Is there something on your mind?

I wonder how the sea would look
in a photo when it's dark~

────Hmm...
Well, it might look dark and a little scary.

Hinana's face probably wouldn't be visible
in the darkness either.

Eh~~~
I wouldn't like that at all~

Haha, yeah. It would be nice to come back
during the daytime when the sun is out.
